title: Hour 3 – LIVE Reaction to the Carson Wentz Trade! Guest – Will Blackmon
itunes:title: Hour 3 – LIVE Reaction to the Carson Wentz Trade! Guest – Will Blackmon
description:
Doug Gottlieb and Rob Parker and react live to breaking news that the Eagles have agreed to trade Carson Wentz to the Indianapolis Colts! They weigh in on the best possible scenario for the Pittsburgh Steelers this offseason. Plus, Super Bowl champion Will Blackmon stops by to discuss whether or not the Rams need to win a Super Bowl for the Matthew Stafford trade to be considered a ‘success.’
